## Architecture Overview

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              CLIENT (React + Vite)           │
│  11 Pages: Dashboard, Coach, Workouts,      │
│  Nutrition, Metrics, Runs, Profile, Auth     │
│  TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui + Recharts         │
└──────────────────┬──────────────────────────┘
                   │ REST + GraphQL
┌──────────────────▼──────────────────────────┐
│          EXPRESS BACKEND (Port 4000)         │
│                                             │
│  REST Routes:     │  GraphQL:               │
│  • auth           │  • getDashboardSummary  │
│  • workouts       │                         │
│  • nutrition      │  AI Agent (Gemini 2.5): │
│  • metrics        │  • ReAct loop (5 turns) │
│  • exercises      │  • 4 tools              │
│  • runs/strava    │  • Memory extractor     │
│  • user           │  • Helicone observability│
│                                             │
│  Middleware: JWT auth, Zod, Rate limit      │
└────────┬─────────────────┬──────────────────┘
         │                 │
    ┌────▼────┐      ┌─────▼─────┐
    │  MySQL  │      │   Redis   │
    │  (RDS)  │      │(ElastiCache)│
    │ 12 tables│     │ Auth + Cache│
    └─────────┘      └───────────┘
```

```
AWS Target Architecture (ECS Fargate):

   Route 53 → CloudFront → S3 (React SPA)
                         → ALB → ECS Fargate (Express)
                                      ├── RDS MySQL (private subnet)
                                      └── ElastiCache Redis (private subnet)
   Terraform IaC: VPC + 5 modules
   CI/CD: 3 GitHub Actions workflows
```

