## Tech Stack Summary

| Layer | Technology | Key Decision |
|-------|-----------|-------------|
| Frontend | React 19 + Vite + TypeScript + TailwindCSS v4 | shadcn/ui for component library |
| API | Hybrid GraphQL (Apollo) + REST | GraphQL for dashboard, REST for auth/CRUD |
| Backend | Express + TypeScript | Service-layer architecture |
| ORM | Prisma | Type-safe queries, schema-driven migrations |
| Validation | Zod | Runtime validation on all endpoints |
| Database | MySQL 8 | 12-table normalized schema + strategic JSON |
| Cache | Redis 7 | Refresh tokens + dashboard caching |
| AI Model | Google Gemini 2.5 Flash | Agentic tool-calling with ReAct loop |
| AI Memory | Custom dual-LLM extraction | TTL-based fact management |
| Observability | Helicone | LLM call monitoring and cost tracking |
| Containers | Docker Compose | Dev: MySQL + Redis. Prod: 5-service setup |
| IaC | Terraform (modular) | VPC, RDS, ECS, ElastiCache, S3 modules |
| CI/CD | GitHub Actions (planned) | 3 independent workflows |
| Cloud | AWS (ECS Fargate) | Managed compute, DB, cache, CDN |
